com.complexible.common.cache
Class Caches

java.lang.Object
  com.complexible.common.cache.Caches

public class Caches
extends Object

Utility class that can be used to create LRU caches. The caches returned implements the Map interface but does not necessarily the views that supports iteration (e.g. Map.entrySet()).

2.1
